法莱斯在[[柯本气候分类法|柯本气候分类法]]中属于[[温带海洋性气候|温带海洋性气候]]<ref name="climat">{{Cite web|url=https://www.infoclimat.fr/climatologie/normales-records/1981-2010/radome-damblainville/valeurs/MF14216001.html|title=Station météorologique de RADOME DAMBLAINVILLE|accessdate=2021-01-17|language=fr|website=infoclimat.fr|dead-url=no|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122052650/https://www.infoclimat.fr/climatologie/normales-records/1981-2010/radome-damblainville/valeurs/MF14216001.html}}</ref>。

